Package: goshs
Version: 2.1.4
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: git, golang
Section: net
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://goshs.de/
Description: Feature-rich single-binary file server for red teamers and developers
 Goshs is a powerful HTTP/S · WebDAV · FTP/SFTP · SMB · LDAP/S server.
 It supports NTLM hash capture, DNS/SMTP callbacks, TLS, authentication,
 and share links – a robust replacement for python3 -m http.server.
